Name: Dave-Man
About the game: Inspired by real life events in an office . . . Coffee Dave Needs His Coffee . . . Not Chatty Cathy! You must help Dave get his coffee each level by collecting all the coffee beans and making it to the coffee maker without getting caught by Chatty Cathy in PacMan inspired gameplay. You succeed, you get paid. You fail? . . . there's always tomorrow What Next? Go home. Buy stuff online. Eat dinner with the wife. Then repeat . . . until retirement. Retirement . . . Now What? That is the real question, isn't it? Make sure you make enough money and buy everything you need to keep you entertained in retirement! By The Numbers Story Mode and Arcade Mode 32 Purchase-able Items 25 NPCs to discover at the water cooler 12 Power Ups to Rout Chatty Cathy 7 Tunes to groove to during normal levels; 15 tracks total in game 70 different floors (aka levels) Development by Lou Bagel, including art, programming, and game design. Audio by Scowsh, including Soundtrack and Sound Effects.
